(154, 3, 1, '', '2014-11-05 10:47:02', 568, 2246, 'bcce5dc4b02fff4a3a1d6b5b5cf27a846e283490', '{"id":3,"asset_id":"314","title":"Full ACL support","alias":"full-acl-support","introtext":"<p>IMC3 fully supports Joomla3 Access Control List (ACL) to set permissions even to lower issue level. Possibilities are amazing. You can define your company\\/authority\\/municipality chart and set who manages what, define if users are allowed to edit issues or edit just their own issues. Set level of administration to each department and even create issues that are only visible to administrators. You can set global, category and issue permissions per user, group or access level. You name it!<\\/p>","fulltext":"","state":1,"catid":"21","created":"2014-11-04 15:29:32","created_by":"568","created_by_alias":"","modified":"2014-11-05 10:47:02","modified_by":"568","checked_out":"568","checked_out_time":"2014-11-05 10:46:42","publish_up":"2014-11-04 15:29:32","publish_down":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","images":"{\\"image_intro\\":\\"images\\\\\\/icons\\\\\\/acl.png\\",\\"float_intro\\":\\"right\\",\\"image_intro_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_caption\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"float_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_caption\\":\\"\\"}","urls":"{\\"urla\\":false,\\"urlatext\\":\\"\\",\\"targeta\\":\\"\\",\\"urlb\\":false,\\"urlbtext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetb\\":\\"\\",\\"urlc\\":false,\\"urlctext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetc\\":\\"\\"}","attribs":"{\\"show_title\\":\\"\\",\\"link_titles\\":\\"\\",\\"show_tags\\":\\"\\",\\"show_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"info_block_position\\":\\"\\",\\"show_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_author\\":\\"\\",\\"link_author\\":\\"\\",\\"show_create_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_modify_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publish_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_item_navigation\\":\\"\\",\\"show_icons\\":\\"\\",\\"show_print_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_email_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show_vote\\