(161, 11, 1, '', '2014-11-05 11:02:43', 568, 2511, '527df327bec77cddccd64d552859f458b2de8c20', '{"id":11,"asset_id":"322","title":"API \\/ REST with Quota","alias":"api-rest-with-quota","introtext":"<p>The full IMC functionalities are wrapped and are available as REST services to developers. That gives ultimate freedom and only imagination is the limit of what can be achieved. Special attention is given to security and now is possible to define unlimited number of secret API keys. This way, administrators are able to measure service requests per client. For example you can define different keys for iPhone and Android mobile IMC applications or create a demo key to give away for test purposes. For each key you can define a quota in terms of requests number in order to limit service invocation and have full control. Every issue and log contains the secret key being used thus leading to better analytics and statistics.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0<\\/p>","fulltext":"","state":1,"catid":"21","created":"2014-11-04 16:59:24","created_by":"568","created_by_alias":"","modified":"2014-11-05 11:02:43","modified_by":"568","checked_out":"568","checked_out_time":"2014-11-05 11:02:29","publish_up":"2014-11-04 16:59:24","publish_down":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","images":"{\\"image_intro\\":\\"images\\\\\\/icons\\\\\\/gears.png\\",\\"float_intro\\":\\"right\\",\\"image_intro_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_caption\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"float_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_caption\\":\\"\\"}","urls":"{\\"urla\\":false,\\"urlatext\\":\\"\\",\\"targeta\\":\\"\\",\\"urlb\\":false,\\"urlbtext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetb\\":\\"\\",\\"urlc\\":false,\\"urlctext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetc\\":\\"\\"}","attribs":"{\\"show_title\\":\\"\\",\\"link_titles\\":\\"\\",\\"show_tags\\":\\"\\",\\"show_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"info_block_position\\":\\"\\",\\"show_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"